{"tid":878686,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【安樂死‧巡迴展覽】安樂死機器「Sarco」下週起第一次在澳洲展出","createTime":"2018-10-27T10:25:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-27T11:24:15.000Z","uid":160807,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4946981306fb5d0bad4cf5e42751372dad04253f","tid":878686,"uid":160807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T10:25:23.000Z","msg":"3D-printable suicide machine on show<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.theaustralian.com.au/national-affairs/health/3dprintable-suicide-machine-on-show/news-story/d1526186630c2f3e1bcbc55e026abbaa\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theaustralian.com.au%2Fnational-affairs%2Fhealth%2F3dprintable-suicide-machine-on-show%2Fnews-story%2Fd1526186630c2f3e1bcbc55e026abbaa&d=SjSrfsubTY%2Blp9nyk2rNPZnkJiu3DM%2BvEze6mtExKRo%3D&h=dd1a37ba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.theaustralian.com.au/national-affairs/health/3dprintable-suicide-machine-on-show/news-story/d1526186630c2f3e1bcbc55e026abbaa</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.newsapi.com.au/image/v1/49e96f299bc748cd5bd8fa47c9b057f1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.newsapi.com.au%2Fimage%2Fv1%2F49e96f299bc748cd5bd8fa47c9b057f1&h=9ea38a5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nThe Sarco assisted suicide machine.<br />\n<br />\n世界上第一台3D打印的安樂死機器將於下週在澳大利亞巡迴展出，瑞士死亡人權組織「Exit International」的創辦人Philip Nitschke博士希望它能吸引維多利亞州的民眾在新的安樂死法律下尋求&ldquo;優雅而時尚的死亡&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n這台名為「Sarco」的機器具有一個可重複使用的光滑膠囊。置身其中的人，使用者爬進去便可按下開關，讓艙內充滿氮氣。機器允許使用者升高坐位看一下&ldquo;最後的世界&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n「Sarco」的膠囊可以拆卸下來直接作為棺材使用。<br />\n<br />\nNitschke博士說，維多利亞州的安樂死立法通過，這將允許一些人選擇他們的死亡時間，&ldquo;因為自殺不是犯罪，但維多利亞州的法律把注意力集中在這個問題上，特別當人們在艱苦的生活條件&ldquo;。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.limitlessiq.com/media/wysiwyg/201804/20180427/895-4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.limitlessiq.com%2Fmedia%2Fwysiwyg%2F201804%2F20180427%2F895-4.jpg&h=37f48917&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但維多利亞州的患者基本上需要得到醫生的許可才能使用新的安樂死法律。他們還必須證明他們可能還有不到六個月的生命。Nitschke博士說：&ldquo;我相信很多人會認為Sarco是另一種理想的選擇。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n「Sarco」提供 VR 裝置，讓民眾體驗進入膠囊後，帶領民眾體驗使用 Sarco 安寧邁向死亡的最後一刻，「你會看見美麗、安寧的大海，真的非常平靜」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.limitlessiq.com/media/wysiwyg/201804/20180427/895-2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.limitlessiq.com%2Fmedia%2Fwysiwyg%2F201804%2F20180427%2F895-2.jpg&h=f19b8090&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">第一場演示將於10月29日在澳洲亞德萊德舉行，其次是珀斯，坎培拉和澳洲悉尼。</span><br />\n<br />\n有冇人有興趣去澳洲睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51b6cec6aea2baace383edff33fa4999ad1a9eb7","tid":878686,"uid":63154,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T10:30:21.000Z","msg":"呢個係繼iPhone後又一個震撼產品，應該好似apple咁整個發佈會先足以表達佢嘅重要性"},{"pid":"f96fe5c71e4ac5f312323c207cb9a34087a72014","tid":878686,"uid":42921,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T10:32:30.000Z","msg":"大過香港啲籠屋"},{"pid":"09c4e4303aa759b8e701659478041c08635d257a","tid":878686,"uid":160807,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T10:35:14.000Z","msg":"如果反應熱烈，相信有機會來香港展出<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a6c5b773a05fa25c9290ccf713b3d5df3515eba","tid":878686,"uid":42921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"09c4e4303aa759b8e701659478041c08635d257a","tid":878686,"uid":160807,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T10:35:14.000Z","msg":"如果反應熱烈，相信有機會來香港展出<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T10:37:05.000Z","msg":"香港政府要你做奴隸，唔會俾展出<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42060db10e7ee3238edc295ee5ff713417e4a401","tid":878686,"uid":160807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3a6c5b773a05fa25c9290ccf713b3d5df3515eba","tid":878686,"uid":42921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"09c4e4303aa759b8e7016